{"tid":560972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教大迫害學生","createTime":"2018-02-14T14:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T15:31:57.000Z","uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d711cddbc063cb0d95d5992f1b038ce7a7fc5b7","tid":560972,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"教育大學兩名學生早前張貼冒犯教育局副局長蔡若蓮的標語，校長張仁良表示，已經嚴正處理，他相信對兩人升學就業有一定影響，據了解兩人沒有被開除出校。<br />\n<br />\n去年九月蔡若蓮喪子當日，教育大學民主牆出現冒犯字句，事隔五個月，校長張仁良表示，已經罰了該兩名並非主修教育的學生。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩名學生沒有被開除出校，張仁良在多番追問下，都沒有透露怎樣罰，指每年都有學生被罰，都不會公開罰則和身份，今次不會、將來亦不會，他指事後逐個辦學團體約見解釋，而去學校實習的學生普遍獲得正面評價，沒有受事件影響，張仁良表示不會收回民主牆，但會跟學生會商討如何改善管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/521635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F521635&d=WUfkuiblbtkL1jM0ISCtEU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5c73a71a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F521635&h=b3ec404e\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/521635</a>"},{"pid":"a013e3eedfadf9e1ec2c46d7989fe935a44d9dcc","tid":560972,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:07:25.000Z","msg":"浸大民主牆直情出「錢小康四字真言」喎.......點罰？"},{"pid":"c4d7f013db0241c6a46df0a0abdb1c95328a1817","tid":560972,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:26:29.000Z","msg":"劉曉波呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e0822c00e95f0cf7644b5c48be1b822fc7c567","tid":560972,"uid":41888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"咁貼劉曉波既學生呢? 又有冇罰呀!?"}]}